Description:
As you walk, searching for a place in the shade from the Ulminin sun, you notice a nearby wall with letters and symbols engraved on it. One of the images catches your eye.

The design resembles the crest you found in Senenthia, though it is not an exact match. Unfortunately, the symbols on the wall are too eroded to confirm any specific details.

It appears that a story is written on this wall, and it might be connected to the crest you discovered.
